<div id="content_block-260309" class="content_block flush title center_align">

  <div class="content_inner_wrapper">

    <div class="custom-title">
      The 100 best needle drops in film and television history
    </div>

    <div class="custom-description">
      From Britney Spears in <i>Spring Breakers</i> to five seconds of Pharoah Sanders in <i>The Sopranos</i>, these are The FADER’s favorite musical cues.
    </div>

    <div class="custom-attribution">
        <div class="author">
    <span>
      By <span class="credit_name"><a href="/contributor/jordan-darville">Jordan Darville</a>, <a href="/contributor/nadine-smith">Nadine Smith</a>, <a href="/contributor/raphael-helfand">Raphael Helfand</a>, <a href="/contributor/david-renshaw">David Renshaw</a>, <a href="/contributor/sandra-song">Sandra Song</a>, <a href="/contributor/alex-robert-ross">Alex Robert Ross</a>, <a href="/contributor/cady-siregar">Cady Siregar</a></span>
  </div>



    </div>





